    "http://ogp.me/ns#description": [
      {
        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "Come appreciate the music of Bach and experience a musical interlude of his most famous musical pieces.\n\nJohann Sebastian Bach had a musical style that fit in the conventions of his day, emulating Vivaldi in the final stages of the baroque style. Specifically, Bach's style showcases his talent for writing tightly woven music of powerful sonority.\n\nOn"
      }
