        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "Silver Bells! - Brantford Symphony Orchestra"
      }
    ],
    "http://ogp.me/ns#description": [
      {
        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "It's the annual Brantford Symphony Christmas extravaganza! Dust off your bells again and bring them along to ring in the Christmas season with a sleigh full of your favourite Christmas-time music. Our special guests this year – Brantford’s Assumption College Choir!"
      },
      {
        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "It's the annual Brantford Symphony Christmas extravaganza! Dust off your bells again and bring them along to ring in the Christmas season with a sleigh full of your favourite Christmas-time music. Our special guests this year – Brantford’s Assumption College Choir!\n\nCurrent season subscribers can renew their seats from June 10-30, 2016. Tickets to the general"
      }
    ],
