      {
        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "Christmas in the City\nwith Special Guest Juan Chioran\n\nAll your favourite Christmas music, with the Maestro and his fabulous orchestra taking you down memory lane! Joining us is one of the Stratford Festival’s leading performers, tenor Juan Chioran!\n\nSINGLE TICKET PRICES\nAdult Singles: Nov or Dec Concerts $40 or $30, April Concert $30\nStudent Singles: Nov or Dec"
