        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "Christmas Bells with the Elmer Iseler Singers - Brantford Symphony Orchestra"
      }
    ],
    "http://ogp.me/ns#description": [
      {
        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "As always, the Orchestra presents your sentimental favourites in new and exciting arrangements, along with some \"two thumbs up\" chestnuts from years past. Presenting our special guests, one of Canada's most famous choirs, the Elmer Iseler Singers. The seats will go fast and the Sanderson will be packed! Get your tickets early to avoid disappointment!"
      },
      {
        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "As always, the Orchestra presents your sentimental favourites in new and exciting arrangements, along with some \"two thumbs up\" chestnuts from years past. Presenting our special guests, one of Canada's most famous choirs, the Elmer Iseler Singers. The seats will go fast and the Sanderson will be packed! Get your tickets early to avoid disappointment!\n\nBuy"
      }
