        "@value": "Finally, after a year and a half of Covid-19, we can see the light at the end of the tunnel! Let the Brantford Symphony help you put all that anxiety behind with a light and happy program sure to put a smile on your face (even if it’s still under a mask!). There will be"
      }
    ],
