        "@value": "After a pandemic-forced interruption to Brantford’s annual big symphony extravaganza, it’s time to come back! Dust off your bells (remember those?) and bring them along to ring in the Christmas season with a sleigh full of your favourite Christmas-time music. Make up for the time when there"
