      {
        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "Internationally renowned Canadian-born (from London, ON) Violinist Lara St. John kicks off one the Brantford Symphony’s most exciting seasons ever. Lara has appeared with major orchestras across North America and around the world, has been featured in People magazine, US News and World Report, CNN, and CBC, earned rave reviews from prestigious Dailies, and is"
