    "http://ogp.me/ns#description": [
      {
        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "With Strata Vocal Ensemble\n\nChristmas time means many things to us. Candy canes, Christmas trees, presents exchanged, warm and cheerful parties, maybe some snow... For us at the Brantford Symphony, above all it means Christmas and happy seasonal music. And we bring it to you all packaged in one special night, when we search out and"
      }
