    "http://ogp.me/ns#description": [
      {
        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "Featuring pianist Bryn Blackwood\n\nYour concert season begins with a full and satisfying classical orchestra experience. There is a Piano Concerto, performed by an exciting young soloist originally from Simcoe! Bryn Blackwood will keep you mesmerized as he brings French composer Camille Saint-Saëns’ popular Second Concerto to life. Saint-Saëns wrote this piece in only three weeks,"
      }
    ],
