    "http://ogp.me/ns#description": [
      {
        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "With Sultans of String and friends\nCelebrating the arrival to Canada of immigrants from around the world.\nFEATURING Leen Hamo, Majd Sukar, Donné Roberts, Saskia Tomkins, Padideh Ahrarnejad, Tamar Ilana and more. \n\nPRE-CONCERT TALK at 6:55pm (doors open at 6:45pm).\nCome early for a Q & A session with our guest musicians.\n\n\"The Refuge Project is centered around the"
      }
