      {
        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "Join us on July 1st at the Brant Performing Arts booth at Lions Park Steve Brown Sports Complex, discover local performing arts groups, and fill out a ballot to win free tickets to an upcoming performance!\n\nFor more information regarding Brantford’s Canada Day celebration:\nBrantford's Canada Day - City of Brantford"
