    "http://ogp.me/ns#description": [
      {
        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "Join the BSO for “Romantic Horizons” with guest conductor Samuel Tam.\n\nA program celebrating the sweeping emotion and colour of the Romantic symphonic tradition, culminating in Dvořák’s beloved Symphony No. 9, “From the New World.”\n\nTickets for the BSO 2026-27 season will be available for sale starting July 2, 2026 at the Sanderson Centre box office.\n\nMore details"
      }
    ],
